snippet.textDisplay:
As you can tell from my username I'm a massive heavy metal fan, so I don't normally listen to a lot of grime or rap. However I do like Dr Dre, Eminem and sole music especially George Benson.

It's not a total surprise but I was curious so I clicked on the video. After watching this I must say that stormzy is very articulate and should be the next prime minister.

It's a shame because sometimes you have assumptions and stormzy completely proved me wrong. PS I think stormzy should become an after dinner speaker he's very motivational.

I actually think stormzy would be a very good TV presenter maybe for Good Morning Britain or something similar.

He could also be a very good weather presenter... " Today the weather is very stormzy" :)
